
'''= A Libre License is a license which grants users the freedom to read, listen to, watch, or otherwise experience the particular work; to learn from or with it; to copy, adapt and use it for any purpose; and to share derived works for the benefit of the community.'''  [http://wikieducator.org/Barcelona_Charter_for_Innovation_Creativity_and_Access_to_Knowledge_-_Libre_Interpretation]


=Examples=
        
Libre licenses include: 

* [http://creativecommons.org/licenses/sa/1.0/ Creative Commons ShareAlike]
            
* [http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0/ Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike]
            
* [http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0/ Creative Commons Attribution]
            
* [http://www.gnu.org/copyleft/fdl.html GNU Free Documentation License]. 


